  "detailed_description": "A combination of Breakout, Shoot Em Up, and Baseball, Aliens Go Home Run puts you in the shoes of Sally, a young girl with a passion for baseball. When she hits a home run so hard, the ball flies into space and crashes into a faraway planet belonging to an alien race, creating a crater in the process. Now, the aliens are taking revenge on Earth, and its up to Sally to save the day!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features include:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>70 levels of Brick-Breaking Action!<br></li><li>9 Intense Boss Fights<br></li><li>Several different power-ups and enemy types<br></li><li>Awesome chiptune soundtrack by +TEK<br></li><li>Online leaderboards to compare your level scores against the world!<br></li><li>A robust Level Editor with Steam Workshop support</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "A combination of Breakout, Shoot Em Up, and Baseball, Aliens Go Home Run puts you in the shoes of Sally, a young girl with a passion for baseball. When she hits a home run so hard, the ball flies into space and crashes into a faraway planet belonging to an alien race, creating a crater in the process. Now, the aliens are taking revenge on Earth, and its up to Sally to save the day!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features include:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>70 levels of Brick-Breaking Action!<br></li><li>9 Intense Boss Fights<br></li><li>Several different power-ups and enemy types<br></li><li>Awesome chiptune soundtrack by +TEK<br></li><li>Online leaderboards to compare your level scores against the world!<br></li><li>A robust Level Editor with Steam Workshop support</li></ul>",
